    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">To be fair, this approach is not so effective as of today because many information gets lost when mapping the neuron states to get logical predicates. Here is where the hope lives to find a solution to exactly such problems and make the dream of AI reality.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
